// An if/else whose arms each fall into a separate infinite loop that never re-converges.
// The original CFG has two disjoint terminal SCCs ({1} and {2}); `add_infinite_loop_post_dominators`
// picks the highest-rank input node from each terminal SCC (here 1 and 2 respectively) and adds
// an impossible edge to each, so both regions get post-dominators.
//
//       0
//      / \
//   ->1   2<-
//    \_|  |_/

cond,0,1,2
code,1,1
code,2,2
